## 24HG Forge — Lorax post-install template
## Customizes the ISO boot environment with Forge branding

## Replace Fedora product name references
replace "Fedora" "24HG Forge" /etc/os-release
replace "Fedora" "24HG Forge" /usr/lib/os-release

## Set product name for Anaconda
append /etc/anaconda/product.d/forge.conf "[Product]\nproduct_name = 24HG Forge\n"
